body:
Hey, can someone good with anatomy point out the flaws to me on this sketch

LIKE ,,, especially on the left arm how am i supposed to get it to not look like that

Any artist wanting to share some criticism or advice is welcome! also its uh light nsfw since the sketch is of a naked dood but its really a sketch so there’s not much to look at lmao. It’s like a naked ken doll with f*ed up anatomy

I’m especially interested to hear about any proportion problems since that seems to be my biggest flaw, and arms/legs anatomy. But if you notice any other flaws (outside the face pls i made no effort on that one lmao) feel free to tell me about it! I want to improve my anatomy skills so ive been reading/watching a lot of tutorials but I still can’t will my hand to cooperate. Any tips appreciated!!!

summary:
Heyyyy, I'm opening my very first commission that uses actual money wow.
I'm currently studying at a University right now,...
body:
Heyyyy, I’m opening my very first commission that uses actual money wow.

I’m currently studying at a University right now, especially when the course I’m in is Art. You know how expensive art supplies are.

Even if you can’t commission me, sharing/reblogging this post is appreciated!

+ PRICES +

–>LINEART + CELL SHADE

-HEADSHOT(3 USD/MYR)

-HALFBODY (8 USD/MYR)

-FULLBODY (10 USD/MYR)

–>LINEART + FULL COLOUR

-HEADSHOT (8 USD/MYR)

-HALFBODY (10 USD/MYR)

-FULLBODY (15 USD/MYR)

—-

–>LINELESS + CELL SHADE

-HEADSHOT (10 USD/MYR)

-HALFBODY (15 USD/MYR)

-FULLBODY (20 USD/MYR)

–>LINELESS + FULL COLOUR

-HEADSHOT (15 USD/MYR)

-HALFBODY (20 USD/MYR)

-FULLBODY (25 USD/MYR)

++10 USD/MYR FOR EVERY CHARACTER ADDITION!!++

—-

(WHAT I CAN DRAW)

+HUMANOIDS. I work best with poc characters. But any human is welcome.

+ANTHROS. Furries are my forte and I highly encourage this lmao.

+MECHAS. I may not post a lot about it. But I can draw em’.

+Although I didn’t write it in the picture, I can also draw monsters, demons and etc.

+I can do SIMPLE BACKGROUNDS. Such as simple floating flowerbed, skies, ocean and etc.

+I can do any romantic COUPLES. (However I will not draw them kissing as I’m not very good at drawing them)

+MILD GORE. Such as cuts, blood spills, missing eyeball but we can discuss this and see what’s in both of our comfort zone)

(WHAT I CAN’T DRAW)

-NSFW as in porn lmao. I mean I can do mild lewd stuffs but anything that shows off nipples (no matter the gender) or genitalia, is a big no no.

-HATE ART. Buddy, if you think I’d promote your hateful propaganda through my art then you’re outta luck, bucko.

-DETAILED BACKGROUNDS. I’m not really the best when it comes to background. But we can discuss about this and see what’s in both of our comfort zone.

-GROSS STUFF. It’s the same with hate art. But I refuse to draw anything that has to do with pedophilia, sexualizing minors, transphobia and any form of hate that ridicules and erases an individual’s identity.

NOTE : If I find my commission very difficult to do, I will decline it. Forgive me, I’m still learning.

!!(HOW TO COMMISH ME)!!

1) Email me! ikanbiris@gmail.com or shoot me a dm via the messenger at my FB art page (canned+fish) or my tumblr. Please avoid sending comments or asks.

Friends however, are allowed to message my personal accounts.

2) Provide me a full reference of your character(s).

3) Give me the backgrounds of the character(s) and their personality if they’re your original character(s) or from a show.

4) Or you can tell me how I should draw them. From poses, expressions, settings and many more.

5) I will send you a sketch first, assuring you of my job. However, I will not resume my progress until you’ve payed me upon seeing the sketch.

6) For Malaysians, you can send me the money locally. For those who wants to pay me via Paypal, you can send it to ikanbiris@gmail.com

7) You are given a week to pay me after receiving the sketch. Unless a payment plan has been discussed.

This is a random blog about randomness shit.
Art/Ask/RP/18+ blog/Multifandom
Post are mostly drawn and/or written.
There will be gore, dark themes, and cursing. But mostly just funny shit.
I draw video games, IRL stuff, random fandoms and NSFW, sometimes. Lots of stuff really.
Response is usually fast unless I'm doing something. Might have to wait for an hour or so. But if it's something big, like going to the hospital or a tragedy, I usually post about it after the event has passed or when it's less stressful.
Roleplay is private (NSFW and/or SFW). I RP mostly one liners to paragraphs. Genre is an open bag for me.
Also sorry for the bad art. I'm just using what I have and to the best of my ability.
Anonymous are allowed!
(Description may change randomly. Scatter brained a bit.)
Enjoy!
